Stump
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.ItemSelectable, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.SwingConstants
public class Stump
extends javax.swing.JButton
Models a stump. This class represents a JButton object of a stump. When combined with the Create map class, instances of the Stump class can be displayed on the window.
Author:
Yuhao Zhu
